Package org.shanerx.tradeshop.objects

This class contains all the classes of the core of the plugin. The reason we are adding them to the docs are that the custom event framework makes use of the Shop class, and should only be used for read purposes, ie. accessing getters. NOTE: DO NOT ATTEMPT TO CHANGE THE PLUGIN'S INTERNAL DATA, NOT EVEN WITH SETTER METHODS, IF YOU DO NOT POSSESS AN UNDERSTANDING OF THE INTERNAL WORKINGS OF THE PLUGIN!
